# EVI dev bridge

- **EVI (`agent-api`)**: runtime productivity — tools, `/chat`, n8n webhooks, notes, WhatsApp processor tests.
- **Cursor Agent**: implement and refactor code in this repo; use codebase-memory MCP first.
- **Copilot CLI**: `scripts/copilot-dev-runner.sh` for explain/scaffold/debug — not for user-facing agent replies.

See [docs/dev-workflow.md](../../docs/dev-workflow.md).
